\par Our Father, Who art in the Heavens, hallowed be Thy Name. Thy Kingdom come, Thy will be done, on earth as it is in Heaven. Give us this day our daily b
read, and forgive us our debts, as we forgive our debtors; and lead us not into temptation, but deliver us from the evil one. 
